Sentence:
In Palestine he was no longer safe;
 but the tender Theodora revealed his danger, and accompanied
 his flight.

Several of the Roman princes had been blessed with an heir;
 but this peculiar surname was first applied to Constantine
 the Seventh.

The sea was still open for his retreat;
 but the news of the revolution had flown along the coast;
 when fear had ceased, obedience was no more: the Imperial
 galley was pursued and taken by an armed brigantine; and the
 tyrant was dragged to the presence of Isaac Angelus, loaded
 with fetters, and a long chain round his neck.
